; Turan_Asb_Savar (Turan horse archer) — mirror of Iran Asb-savar Kamandar.
; Key is &"turan_asb_savar" (shorter than Iran's compound name).
; RPS folding: _resolve_key("turan_asb_savar") → strips prefix → "asb_savar" →
;   _turan_base_to_iran_key("asb_savar") → &"asb_savar_kamandar" row.
; Rationale for shortened key: avoids &"turan_asb_savar_kamandar" verbosity;
;   the "kamandar" suffix is understood from context. Documented here and in
;   combat_matrix.gd::_turan_base_to_iran_key for future maintainers.
[sub_resource type="Resource" id="unit_turan_asb_savar"]
